{
  "stem": "26728.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and it was just a room about like this, maybe a little bit bigger.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Concrete walls, concrete floors, concrete ceilings, shower heads.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It said [GERMAN] on the shower heads.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we left there and went to the next room, which was the crematorium, which still had the corpses in the partially decom-- cremated in the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in this-- in this crematorium, there was kind of like a sub floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was full of bits of cremated bodies, parts like little bone chips and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So evidently what they did when they were finished was they would just kind of shove all the ashes out one end and it would go through this grating in the sub floor, and then guys on the outside would shovel it into a cart or something and take it away.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used it for manure, for-- for fertilizer, for slippery places.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- you know, these were bodies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These were people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used it as kind of like gravel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's-- that's, you know, awesome to think about that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But later, by now it's getting late in the afternoon, maybe 3:30, 4 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And things have quieted down considerable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had been to the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We'd been to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He took me to-- OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was the most-- the hardest thing for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this is where I just-- I cracked up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we went into a subcamp of Dachau which was separated by gates and fences.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You couldn't get in, had double fences and, you know, the kind with a hook on them like this, which meant they were barbed-wire fence-- I mean electrified fences.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and a double set of gates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we went in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
